videoDetails.Title: The Tank Everyone Forgets
videoDetails.Description:
Decal link: https://tinyurl.com/42thwzv3

The American M47 medium tank is one of the more underrated tanks in War Thunder. It doesn't have much going for it, but it is very reactive and works quite well. If you're grinding the US tech tree, I would recommend trying it.

Check the channel "About" section for the link to the creator of my profile picture.

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/spookston
